\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Broaden - benchmark measurement-claim precision (correctness)\",\"dimensions\":[\"correctness\"],\"filesReviewed\":[\"012-gpt-claude-benchmark/benchmark-results.md\"],\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm-max-1782930580740-aqrcsz\",\"parentSessionId\":null,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"generation\":1,\"continuedFromRun\":null,\"findingsCount\":1,\"findingsSummary\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":9},\"findingsNew\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":0,\"P2\":1},\"findingDetails\":[{\"id\":\"F010\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"title\":\"Benchmark pass-count (7) doesn't reconcile with enumeration (8) or cell table\",\"dimension\":\"correctness\",\"file\":\"012-gpt-claude-benchmark/benchmark-results.md:65\",\"evidence\":\"S5 pass=7 but enumeration lists 8 cells (context2+research2+review2+ai-council2); S3 table classifies 8-9 pass rows\",\"recommendation\":\"Correct the pass count to match the enumeration/table\",\"disposition\":\"active\",\"findingClass\":\"summary-count-mismatch\",\"scopeProof\":\"benchmark-results.md:65-67 vs :43-54 cell table\",\"affectedSurfaceHints\":[\"benchmark summary\",\"closure evidence\"]}],\"newFindingsRatio\":0.08,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-01T22:00:00Z\",\"durationMs\":65000}\nJSONEOF\necho \"appended iteration 5 delta\"","time":{"start":1782931343326,"end":1782931343327}},"id":"prt_f1efd47cf001FRw5VkyPlISb02","sessionID":"ses_0e10e5929ffe88XcmihhZxWbsA","messageID":"msg_f1efd19d10015S9D0IA3XSqNUk"}}
