\"early-phase cohort 002-006\"]}],\"newFindingsRatio\":0.40,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-01T22:12:00Z\",\"durationMs\":60000}\nJSONEOF\necho \"appended iteration 7 delta\""},"output":"appended iteration 7 delta\n","metadata":{"output":"appended iteration 7 delta\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"cat >> \".opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/review/lineages/glm-max/deep-review-state.jsonl\" <<'JSONEOF'\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"claim_adjudication\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":7,\"passed\":true,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm-max-1782930580740-aqrcsz\",\"generation\":1,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-01T22:12:00Z\",\"notes\":\"F012 P1 packet present and complete\"}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":7,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Broaden - systemic layout-migration drift sweep (traceability)\",\"dimensions\":[\"traceability\"],\"filesReviewed\":[\"<all 17 phase implementation-summaries via grep>\",\"spec.md:74\"],\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm-max-1782930580740-aqrcsz\",\"parentSessionId\":null,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"generation\":1,\"continuedFromRun\":null,\"findingsCount\":1,\"findingsSummary\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":3,\"P2\":9},\"findingsNew\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":0},\"findingDetails\":[{\"id\":\"F012\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"title\":\"Layout-migration drift systemic across phases 002-005 (broken nested packet_pointers)\",\"dimension\":\"traceability\",\"file\":\"003-agent-dispatch-hardening/implementation-summary.md:12\",\"evidence\":\"002-005 impl-summaries all packet_pointer under non-existent 001-deep-agent-router-and-orchestration/00X with off-by-one numbering; 001 and 007-017 correct; spec.md:74 declares flat\",\"recommendation\":\"Regenerate continuity metadata for phases 002-006 via generate-context.js\",\"disposition\":\"active\",\"findingClass\":\"systemic-migration-drift\",\"scopeProof\":\"grep packet_pointer 17 files; grep 001-deep-agent-router-and-orchestration/00[0-9] -> 002,003,004,005,006\",\"affectedSurfaceHints\":[\"resume ladder\",\"packet_pointer navigation\",\"graph traversal\",\"early-phase cohort 002-006\"]}],\"newFindingsRatio\":0.40,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-01T22:12:00Z\",\"durationMs\":60000}\nJSONEOF\necho \"appended iteration 7 delta\"","time":{"start":1782931502556,"end":1782931502558}},"id":"prt_f1effb5cd001RMkIOgarAobxls","sessionID":"ses_0e10e5929ffe88XcmihhZxWbsA","messageID":"msg_f1eff8563001TK3DCJH236ykzP"}}
