{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782931532907,"sessionID":"ses_0e10e5929ffe88XcmihhZxWbsA","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_5426cf4da619421cabad444a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"echo \"=== Does prompt.md still carry the old Mode-D self-classification gate? ===\" && grep -n \"general_agent_verified\\|SELF-CHECK\\|self-classification\\|Are you operating\" .opencode/commands/prompt.md 2>&1 | head -10 && echo \"\" && echo \"=== context for the gate ===\" && grep -n \"general_agent_verified\" .opencode/commands/prompt.md 2>&1"},"output":"=== Does prompt.md still carry the old Mode-D self-classification gate? ===\n27:EXECUTE THIS AUTOMATIC SELF-CHECK (NOT A USER QUESTION):\n29:SELF-CHECK: Are you operating as the @general agent?\n37:│   └─ general_agent_verified = TRUE → Continue to Setup Phase\n58:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n157:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n172:| general_agent_verified | ✅ Yes         | ______     | Automatic check         |\n\n=== context for the gate ===\n37:│   └─ general_agent_verified = TRUE → Continue to Setup Phase\n58:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n157:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n172:| general_agent_verified | ✅ Yes         | ______     | Automatic check         |\n","metadata":{"output":"=== Does prompt.md still carry the old Mode-D self-classification gate? ===\n27:EXECUTE THIS AUTOMATIC SELF-CHECK (NOT A USER QUESTION):\n29:SELF-CHECK: Are you operating as the @general agent?\n37:│   └─ general_agent_verified = TRUE → Continue to Setup Phase\n58:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n157:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n172:| general_agent_verified | ✅ Yes         | ______     | Automatic check         |\n\n=== context for the gate ===\n37:│   └─ general_agent_verified = TRUE → Continue to Setup Phase\n58:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n157:- `general_agent_verified = ________________`\n172:| general_agent_verified | ✅ Yes         | ______     | Automatic check         |\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"echo \"=== Does prompt.md still carry the old Mode-D self-classification gate? ===\" && grep -n \"general_agent_verified\\|SELF-CHECK\\|self-classification\\|Are you operating\" .opencode/commands/prompt.md 2>&1 | head -10 && echo \"\" && echo \"=== context for the gate ===\" && grep -n \"general_agent_verified\" .opencode/commands/prompt.md 2>&1","time":{"start":1782931532905,"end":1782931532906}},"id":"prt_f1f002c5e001O2Q484Cam2n80m","sessionID":"ses_0e10e5929ffe88XcmihhZxWbsA","messageID":"msg_f1effede00011HBgQZownyC3Xg"}}
